{"tid":715482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到英格蘭對巴拿馬有感而發","createTime":"2018-06-24T13:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T16:37:24.000Z","uid":139139,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"28014b2432118579ebc1182ec7b41540cfa204d1","tid":715482,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"雖然巴拿馬抵死<br />\n但係佢啲觀眾都仲係好支持佢哋<br />\n一次入球全場尖叫<br />\n突然之間喺度諗<br />\n如果香港有機會打世界盃<br />\n我諗上半場炒咗五粒<br />\n起碼有香港人觀眾七成已經走咗<br />\n之後一路踢一路屌鳩佢哋<br />\n香港人心態真係有問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/214009_308685ea642c7310493f183e5cb35319.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F214009_308685ea642c7310493f183e5cb35319.gif&h=427ee143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"396aad65725fd39621e888077bda8a2a0b7624b0","tid":715482,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"人地英格蘭入到一波已經好滿足"},{"pid":"676a694d0dd78f5b4644a52649b6fa5b603d470e","tid":715482,"uid":139139,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"396aad65725fd39621e888077bda8a2a0b7624b0","tid":715482,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"人地英格蘭入到一波已經好滿足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"香港人就係有錢齊齊分<br />\n有難就走先<br />\n<br />\n就算入咗一球都會話<br />\n入一球有乜嘢用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家輸緊六球"},{"pid":"413380a5ccd87965c100ab070134995f468894eb","tid":715482,"uid":55555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"淨係識開post假設乜乜乜 借啲意踩低香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前世界盃外圍賽對卡塔爾輸到0：3，大部分球迷咪又係繼續打氣，就算最後輸2：3都無你所講「咪又係輸」嘅言論。<br />\n我相信如果香港隊有朝一日入到決賽週，每個球員都搏盡嘅話，無論結果係點，香港人一定會撐佢哋。"},{"pid":"b2c67ba75f0f9e6297aa2ab0703808fc1a21c4d4","tid":715482,"uid":167465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"你自己都係到踩緊香港人 <br />\n<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426ee75b719bd35e15698b8c97232201915968e5","tid":715482,"uid":3523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"你都好撚抵死"}]}